<h3>POST /api/contacts</h3>
<div>
  Create contact
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
  http://localhost:3000/api/contacts
</div>
<b>Example request</b>
<div>
  curl -X POST -H 'Authorization: Bearer auth_token' -H "Content-Type: application/json" --data '{ "contact": {"subject": "welcome", "message": "Hi"} }' "http://localhost:3000/api/contacts"
  <br/>
  auth_token: jwt token of current user
</div>
